title: Athletic Club vs Barcelona - Spanish La Liga 2024/2025
description: Athletic have won just one of their last 22 matches against FC Barcelona in LaLiga, 1-0 in August 2019 on the opening day of the season, and have also failed to score in five of their last six league meetings. title: Brighton and Hove Albion vs. Liverpool - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Having lost four of their first five Premier League home games against Liverpool, Brighton are now unbeaten in their last two against the Reds at the Amex Stadium in the competition. Liverpool have won their last two Premier League games against Brighton, having won just one of their previous seven against the Seagulls beforehand.

title: Everton vs. Southampton - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Everton lost their last home league match against Southampton in January 2023, ending a 17-game unbeaten run against Saints at Goodison Park. They last lost consecutive home league games against them in April 1974. Following their 1-0 win at St Mary’s in the reverse fixture, Southampton are looking to complete the league double over Everton for the first time since 1997-98.

title: Crystal Palace vs Manchester City - FA Cup Final - 2024-2025
description: Manchester City are competing in their 14th FA Cup final. They’ve won the trophy seven times, behind only Arsenal, Manchester United, Chelsea, Liverpool and Tottenham. Crystal Palace are competing in their third FA Cup final, losing to Manchester United in both 1990 and 2016. They’re one of four clubs to compete in two finals without ever winning the trophy along with Queen’s Park, Birmingham City and Watford.

description: Live and exclusive action from the EFL (English Football League) One. EFL One is the third-tier in the English football league system. title: Sheffield Utd vs Sunderland - EFL - English Football League - Championship Playoff 2024/25
description: EFL - English Football League - Championship Playoff Final 2024/25Sheffield Utd and Sunderland overcame Bristol City and Coventry City in their respective semi-final ties, and the winners will join Leeds United and Burnley in next season’s English top flight. Sheffield United finished 14 points ahead of Sunderland in the regular Championship season table – it’s the biggest points difference between two English Football League play-off finalists in the current format (since 1988-89).The Blades became just the third side in the history of the second tier to win as many as 90 points yet fail to get promoted automatically, after Sunderland in 1997-98 and Leeds United last season.

The event takes place from May 25 to June 8, 2025. This iconic clay-court championship features top players from around the world competing for glory in singles, doubles, and mixed doubles categories. As always, Roland Garros promises intense competition and unforgettable moments in the world of tennis.

description: The 2025 Roland Garros is the 129th edition of the French Open overall. Within the Open Era, which began in 1968, the 2024 edition is the 58th edition. The event takes place from May 25 to June 8, 2025. This iconic clay-court championship features top players from around the world competing for glory in singles, doubles, and mixed doubles categories. As always, Roland Garros promises intense competition and unforgettable moments in the world of tennis.

title: Match 1 /D3 - Court 14 - Roland Garros - 2025
description: The 2025 Roland Garros is the 129th edition of the French Open overall. Within the Open Era, which began in 1968, the 2024 edition is the 58th edition. The event takes place from May 25 to June 8, 2025. This iconic clay-court championship features top players from around the world competing for glory in singles, doubles, and mixed doubles categories. As always, Roland Garros promises intense competition and unforgettable moments in the world of tennis.

description: Doha hosts the prestigious ITTF World Table Tennis Championships Finals for the second time, bringing together the worlds elite players to compete across five events: Mens Singles, Womens Singles, Mens Doubles, Womens Doubles, and Mixed Doubles. title: Nimes vs PSG - LNH Division 1 - French Handball Starligue
description: Dive into the excitement of French handball with Liqui Moly Starligue, formerly LNH Division 1. Established in 1952, this premier league event features 16 top teams battling for glory. Champions earn spots in the EHF Champions League, while cup winners qualify for the European League.

title: Tales of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Raph Thinks It Through
description: Raphs strength wont save him when hes caught between the Mechazoids and the notorious street gang known as Purple Dragons! Raphs going to have to use his head to get out of this one!

title: Tales of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Donnie Hangs Tough
description: Its a battle of the wits between Donnie and Bishop as he races through NYCs subway system to stop her evil Mechazoids. But how do you beat an AI that counters your every move?

title: The Twisted Timeline of Sammy and Raj: Bollyweird / The Spied Who Bugged Me
description: Follow the laugh-out-loud time-altering adventures of Sammy and Raj, as they pause, rewind, fast-forward and slow down their reality with the help of a mysterious phone app.

title: The Penguins Of Madagascar: Littlefoot / Smotherly Love
description: Marlene is dying to go see a concert in the park. But, every time she leaves the zoo she becomes a feral monster!  Ma, an empty-nested mother possum, takes up residence in the Penguins Lair after they destroy her home.

title: The Penguins Of Madagascar: A Kipper For Skipper / High Moltage
description: Its off to the races when Skipper agrees to give a day off from hard training to the first penguin who can bring him a kipper.  The penguins are determined to make opening day of their favorite action stars blockbuster movie!

title: The Penguins Of Madagascar: Operation: Big Blue Marble
description: The Penguins are faced with a global battle when their specialty food-making machine belches out a toxic cloud that threatens not just the zoo, not just the city, but the earth itself!

title: The Penguins Of Madagascar: Feline Fervor / Action Reaction
description: King Julien is literally bounced out of his kingdom and onto the New York streets.  Skipper is forced to live his worst nightmare when hes doused with Inflatium and stress causes him to blow up like a balloon.

title: Best and Bester: Thats So Cupid / Buddy Odour
description: Best and Bester are a pair of hilariously individual twins who live in a weird and wonderful alternate reality where your neighbour could be a pair of disgruntled trousers or your best friend a floating cloud of bottom burp.

title: Best and Bester: Fight or Flight / Employee of the Month
description: Best and Bester are a pair of hilariously individual twins who live in a weird and wonderful alternate reality where your neighbour could be a pair of disgruntled trousers or your best friend a floating cloud of bottom burp.

description: Leo takes the Turtles to train in the woods in an advanced ninja ritual where they must overcome their weaknesses and face their greatest enemies in order to become true ninjas.

description: The kids turn against Sanjay when he maroons them all on a highway median in Traffical Island, and then in Partybot, Sanjay and Craig find an old robot and become party animals.

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Mermaidman Begins / Planktons Good Eye
description: Mermaidman and Barnacleboy let SpongeBob and Patrick in on their secret, heroic origins!  Using SpongeBobs DNA, Plankton grows himself a second eye and becomes nice!

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Barnacle Face / Pet Sitter Pat

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Chum Caverns
description: Plankton creates an underground restaurant that threatens to put the Krusty Krab out of business.

title: Tales of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Splinter and April Fight a Goldfish
description: When the Lair floods, April goes to save Splinter... but he wont leave the sewer! To make matters worse, the mutant called GOLDFIN comes with a warning... stay out of his way, or else!

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Restraining SpongeBob / Fiasco!
description: Squidward has had enough of SpongeBobs annoying antics and issues a restraining order against him.  Plankton thinks hes stolen a Krabby Patty from the Krusty Krab, but hes really stolen an art piece by the famous artist, Fiasco.

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Are You Happy Now? / Planet Of The Jellyfish
description: When Squidward cant recall his happiest memory, SpongeBob helps him create one.  When an evil Jellien overlord replaces everyone in Bikini Bottom with clones, its up to SpongeBob and Sandy to defeat him!

description: Mermaidman and Barnacleboy let SpongeBob and Patrick in on their secret, heroic origins!

title: Kamp Koral: SpongeBobs Under Years: Helter Shelter / Reveille Revolution
description: SpongeBob, Sandy, and Patrick are split up into separate cabins. // Squidward has to earn back his morning Reveille duties.

description: Still under the effects of Miss Lucass brainwashing program, Anika betrays her family by leading an operation to kidnap Baby Harry, and Florian tries to pull the wool further over Oliver and Jasmyns eyes. Evie, however, grows suspicious.

title: Rock Island Mysteries: The Shadow
description: After a meteorite crashes in the jungle and Taylor accidentally touches it, her shadow breaks free and leads them to the Institutes secret South Section. When Taylor, Nori, and Ellis meet trouble inside, Lila and Meesha must save the day!

title: The Thundermans: Undercover: No Friend In Sight
description: Chloe feels smothered by Max and Phoebe, and encourages them to make new friends. However, the twins unwittingly make the same friend, and begin a battle for the ages over her. Chloes new alone time is interrupted by living room-crashing pelican.

title: The Thundermans: Undercover: All About Steve
description: Billy arrives, hopeful that his new sidekick Steve can join the T-Force. Phoebe and Max consider it, but soon discover that his superpower is making marshmallows. After they reject Steves bid to join the team, he turns evil and vows revenge.

title: Tales of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Leonardo Stands Alone
description: The Ninja Turtles are on the run and...alone. Leonardo is a leader but who is he without anyone to lead? Leo now has to stop Bishop and her Mechazoids while trying to save his brothers.

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Mall Girl Pearl / Two Thumbs Down
description: Pearl gets a job to be cool like her friends, but the only store thats hiring is the lamest store at the mall!  SpongeBob loses the use of his thumbs, and must get them back in working order before his entire life falls apart.

title: The Smurfs: The Talented Justa Smurf/Smurf, Yes Smurf!
description: Justa Smurf, surrounded by others who are all "Something Smurf", is still searching for his calling. // While Papa Smurf is away, Brainy uses a potion to finally get the Village to obey his every whim

title: The Smurfs: Mommys Masterpiece/A Thief Among Us!
description: When the other Smurfs bail out of posing for Painters masterpiece, he finds a new subject in Gargamels Mother. // When the Smurfs favorite things start disappearing all over the Village, everyone gets worried and suspicious.

title: The Casagrandes: Bend It Like Abuelo / Bunstoppable
description: Hector finally joins his dream soccer team as their good luck charm, but what happens when his luck runs out?  While preparing bao for the Chinese Cultural Fair, Sid and Adelaide face off against time-hopping bandits!

title: The Casagrandes: Squawk In The Name Of Love / Date With Destiny
description: Sergio enlists Adelaides help to become a gentleman in order to win Priscilla back!  Rosa hears an Ernesto Estrella prediction that Maria and Arturo could get back together - could it be true?

title: The Casagrandes: Skaters Gonna Hate / Born To Be Mild
description: Ronnie Anne and her pals enlist Carlos X as their coach in a skate-off against Tony Hawk!  Tired of the bullies at school, Alexis learns the tough guy ropes from Carl.

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Mimic Madness / House Worming
description: SpongeBob learns that "imitation is the sincerest form of flattery" - too bad no one told him how to stop!  When worms move into SpongeBobs holes, its up to him to hide his disgusting new friends from everyone else.

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Snooze You Lose / Krusty Katering
description: Squidward is so tired that SpongeBob And Patrick cant wake him up, but they wont let him miss his big audition!  Mr. Krabs And his crew cater a fancy party, but they might be out of their depth with their new wealthy customers.

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Spongebobs Place / Plankton Gets The Boot
description: When SpongeBob cooks at home, Mr. Krabs customers leave his restaurant and head for SpongeBobs Place.  When Plankton gets kicked out of the house, its up to SpongeBob to teach him how to win his computer wife back.

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: The Goobfather
description: Mr. Krabs must reckon with the Goobfather after he adds "Patty Whips" to the menu at the Krusty Krab.

title: The Patrick Star Show: The Wrath of Shmandor / There Goes the Neighborhoo
description: The tiny futuristic city of Shmandor exacts revenge on Patrick Star. // Patrick and Squidina go on location to interview their neighbors.

title: The Casagrandes: Meal Ticket
description: Ronnie Anne and Sid help Casey run his family food truck... at the Yoon Kwon concert!

title: The Casagrandes: Karma Chameleon / Team Effort
description: The Changs go on vacation and leave Ronnie Anne and her cousins to watch after Cam, the chameleon snake.  Ronnie Anne and her skate buddies work together to show their coach that they have what it takes to make a team.

title: The Casagrandes: Chancla Force / Fluff Love
description: Carl takes Rosas chancla, setting off the balance of order in the city, And calling the Chancla Force into action!  Carlitos goes on a wild adventure to get his favorite stuffed animal from the arcade.

title: The Casagrandes: Battle Of The Grandpas / Prankaversary
description: When Fridas fun dad comes to visit, Hector tries to win back his grandchildrens attention.  Ronnie Anne and Lincoln are set for a big day of pranks and newbie Sid wants to join in on the fun too!

title: The Smurfs: The Round Up / Waffle Wednesday
description: Jokey gives Farmers racing snails an extra kick from a magic potion that makes them super fast.  Chef gets jealous when Lily starts to make waffles that are more delicious than his.

title: The Smurfs: Funny Mommy / Smurfy Day Care
description: Jokey transforms Poet into Gargamels Mom, but they find themselves trapped in Gargamels hovel.  Storm has to become a super smurfsitter when all of the Smurfs turn back into babies.

title: Alvinnn!!! And The Chipmunks: The House On Cedar Lane / Bathroom Bully
description: When classmates claim a local haunted house isnt that scary, Alvin decides to prove them wrong.  When Miss Smith praises Simons grades in class, Derek bullies him by not allowing him to use the boys bathroom.

title: Alvinnn!!! And The Chipmunks: The Return Of Thornbergaupht / Squashed
description: Simons interactive video game is about to take off, until Jeanette reprograms the games villain.  When Alvin dreams of joining a private club, he volunteers Dave to play squash, even though Dave doesnt play.

title: ALVINNN!!! and The Chipmunks: Bubble Wrap
description: The Chipmunks and Chipettes are your typical kids. They go to school, have chores and homework, fight like siblings and play sold-out concerts to millions of fans. Oh, did we mention theyre international rock stars?

description: The Casagrandes tells the story of Ronnie Anne, an independent, adventurous, 11-year-old who explores city life with her big, loving, multi-generational Mexican-American family.
